snippet.title: Mislight Trailer #1
snippet.description:
We are four Mexican friends trying to become full-fledged indie video game developers.
Currently working on the adventure-thriller game: “Mislight”.

Wishlist and download the demo on Steam!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2208220/Mislight/

or check out the demo on Itch.io:
https://etherlight.itch.io/mislight

Support Us On Kickstarter!
https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/etherlight/mislight-an-adventure-game-with-a-small-touch-of-thriller

Follow us on Twitter:
https://twitter.com/EtherlightMx

Check out our Instagram Reels:
https://www.instagram.com/etherlightstudios/

We also have a Tiktok!
https://www.tiktok.com/@etherlightstudios

Join Our Community:
https://discord.gg/jdvMCkDQYf
